<section xml:id="restoring-user-interface-defaults" version="5.0" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"
                                                              xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
                                                              xmlns:xl="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" >
  <title>Restoring user interface defaults</title>
  <orderedlist>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        You can restore the default perspective at any time:
      </para>
      
      <para>
        <emphasis role="menupath">Window</emphasis>--&gt;<emphasis role="menupath">Reset Perspective</emphasis>.
      </para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        To show or restore individual views or browsers, choose either the ”<emphasis>restore</emphasis>” icon in the tab for the view or select:
      </para>
        
      <para>
        <emphasis role="menupath">Window</emphasis>--&gt;<emphasis role="menupath">Show View</emphasis>
      </para>
      
      <para>
        and then choose which view to display.
      </para>
    </listitem>
  </orderedlist>
</section>